metadata.name: OBE SHE HE
metadata.description:
18MB – @500psi
3000x3000px

NFT + Physical
Unlock 81MB@1200psi
7100x7100px plus
Archival Pigment print

OBE She He,
With hand extended 
Toward me/you
Says “I’m here 
For you for me.
I am waiting for you
Tough and Strong 
And soft.  
I am after all, 
I’m you, I’m
Everywhere and
All made up of
Consciousness.

This Giant Energy Packet
Came to me during an OBE.
She He, with arms opened 
Showed me a new route.
And I am forever grateful.
